                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tu vas éparpillant tes joies\nSur l'herbe et les talus pierreux,\nMa petite gardeuse d'oies,\nPar les prés et les chemins creux ;"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Et sans penser qu'un jour leurs foies",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Feront des pâtés savoureux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Tu suis tes gros jars bienheureux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Car jamais tu ne les rudoies,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Ma petite gardeuse d'oies.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et sans penser qu'un jour leurs foies\nFeront des pâtés savoureux,\nTu suis tes gros jars bienheureux,\nCar jamais tu ne les rudoies,\nMa petite gardeuse d'oies."
